00:23:45.330 --> 00:23:48.050
to make really good
stories in your life.

00:23:48.050 --> 00:23:51.430
&gt;&gt; Well, I think that's important
that the kids in the audience,

00:23:51.430 --> 00:23:54.570
all the students in the
audience hear your stories

00:23:54.570 --> 00:23:57.970
because I don't know what
perceptions they have of women

00:23:57.970 --> 00:24:03.190 position:56%
in the military, which is kind of
interesting Michael for you that one

00:24:03.190 --> 00:24:08.230
