stories [laughter]?

00:24:38.840 --> 00:24:40.140
Nothing like that.

00:24:40.140 --> 00:24:41.440
&gt;&gt; Did you get your GED?

00:24:41.440 --> 00:24:42.740
&gt;&gt; Yeah, I did get a GED yes,

00:24:42.740 --> 00:24:44.040
because I'm very good
at taking tests.

00:24:44.040 --> 00:24:46.040
Then I went to college and
I dropped out of college.

