00:26:08.600 --> 00:26:12.360
I can make it more interesting,
more accessible maybe.

00:26:12.360 --> 00:26:13.810
I'll add a couple changes.

00:26:13.810 --> 00:26:16.100
I made two big changes
in Front Lines,

