thinking about it,

00:44:46.600 --> 00:44:48.790
job number one is make
your characters real,

00:44:48.790 --> 00:44:51.500
make them authentic
and that's how I start.

00:44:51.500 --> 00:44:54.760
I start with character, then I
go to setting, and from then on,

00:44:54.760 --> 00:44:58.620
