00:47:11.430 --> 00:47:14.600
and along the way I didn't
find anything that I wanted

00:47:14.600 --> 00:47:19.410
to do more I guess, so I know a
lot of friends who fly with me know

00:47:19.410 --> 00:47:21.610 position:56%
who didn't start out wanting to fly.

00:47:21.610 --> 00:47:25.050
They just followed a path
and they end up there.

00:47:25.050 --> 00:47:31.370
I will say that I'll never
be an astronaut at this point

00:47:31.370 --> 00:47:35.600
but it definitely got me
to where I needed to be

00:47:35.600 --> 00:47:38.880
and at this point I really think
that the military for me is kind

00:47:38.880 --> 00:47:41.230
of a calling and I love everything

00:47:41.230 --> 00:47:45.640 position:56%
