they forgot to enjoy the journey

00:48:04.380 --> 00:48:09.680 position:56%
and forgot to do what they wanted to
do along the way so I definitely say

00:48:09.680 --> 00:48:14.250
that for all you guys as you
go through school and college

00:48:14.250 --> 00:48:16.660
