been the best part of that

00:48:36.640 --> 00:48:39.670
and wanting to be an
astronaut got me to that point

00:48:39.670 --> 00:48:41.900
so I'm thankful it's
something that I did stick

00:48:41.900 --> 00:48:44.110
with because it got me
to where I am today.

