obviously not a historian

00:49:11.310 --> 00:49:13.610
or a high school graduate.

00:49:13.610 --> 00:49:14.910
&gt;&gt; You are.

00:49:14.910 --> 00:49:16.210
&gt;&gt; I know.

00:49:16.210 --> 00:49:17.510
&gt;&gt; Now you are.

00:49:17.510 --> 00:49:18.810
&gt;&gt; Well now I am, that's
right, you're right.

00:49:18.810 --> 00:49:21.820
The research part was actually
kind of fun and fun in strange sort

00:49:21.820 --> 00:49:25.540
of ways like for example, I
wanted to be super accurate

00:49:25.540 --> 00:49:28.860
