stuff going okay, if I was walking

00:49:56.100 --> 00:49:59.160
if I wasn't in this car, how
much harder would that be?

00:49:59.160 --> 00:50:00.460
What's the slope like?

00:50:00.460 --> 00:50:02.290
What can I see from here,
what can I see from there?

00:50:02.290 --> 00:50:03.780
That's all kind of neat.

